    secdoc:cellOrder 7 ;
    secdoc:text "A semantic foundation for modeling autonomous and semi-autonomous agents using a clear Agent → Capability → Task hierarchy. Formalizes capabilities as reusable assets, enables inference-based task discovery, and enforces integrity with SHACL. Designed for composable agent ecosystems and extensible governance via layered ontology extensions." .

